/target

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Agent runtimes (local state, not project code)
.omx/
.claude/
.codex/
.opencode/
.gemini/

# DevFlow own state (dogfooding)
.devflow/state.json
.devflow/lock
.devflow/last-ship.json

# DevFlow phase plans (.planning/). The local planning workspace is ignored,
# but the files the launch prompt reads ARE tracked convention — `phase_prompt()`
# reads .planning/ROADMAP.md and .planning/phases/NN-*/CONTEXT.md, so those are
# kept committable. See ARCHITECTURE.md and CONTRIBUTING.md.
.planning/
!.planning/ROADMAP.md
!.planning/PROJECT.md
!.planning/phases/
.planning/phases/*
!.planning/phases/*/CONTEXT.md

# Git worktrees created by `devflow start --worktree` / `parallel` / `sequentagent`
.worktrees/
